summary: Device CA trust verification at rendezvous server
description: |
    Tests device CA certificate trust at rendezvous covering:
    - Device CA certificate registration
    - Trust chain validation during TO1 protocol
    - Certificate verification at rendezvous
    - Untrusted device rejection
    - Certificate-based access control

test: ../../rpm/test-device-ca-rendezvous-trust.sh

framework: shell

duration: 30m

tag:
  - fdo
  - device-ca
  - rendezvous
  - trust
  - certificate
  - rpm
